- the rejection of a period of detention for asylum seekers, especially in âdetention centresâ for illegal immigrants;
- the rejection of the concept of âsafe third countryâ, because the analysis of a period of asylum should take account of each individual case; consequently, the idea of setting up an arbitrary list of countries should be rejected.
After all, on what criteria should such a list be based?
